title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 29 2022
description:
Elon Musk's chart of how the left's gone mad sparks culture war debate. Nancy Pelosi blames high gas prices on price gouging. Buck says, "I just wish Nancy would say things that are amusing, or at least make me think a little bit." Alex Berenson joins Buck to talk about his Twitter lawsuit, the left's abandonment of free speech, Moderna's push to vax kids. Buck takes calls.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
